OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPartly
OL,6,Fcloudy initially then mist and low
OL,7,Fcloud is expected to extend inland
OL,8,Ffrom the coast. Chance of a slight
OL,9,Ffrost, and patchy fog, for any places
OL,10,Fthat remain clear.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FEarly mist, patchy fog or low
OL,13,Fcloud will disperse leaving bright
OL,14,Fconditions as high cloud increases.
OL,15,FChance of an afternoon shower. Rather
OL,16,Fwarm for western places, but cooler
OL,17,Ffurther east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
